data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Appenine Loop is a 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located close to all Lake Nona has to offer. As soon as you enter this 1,759 square foot home, you are greeted with cathedral ceilings and warmth from natural sunlight pouring throughout the space. The open floor plan allows the kitchen to overlook both the living and dining areas. The kitchen features granite countertops, breakfast bar, set in sink, stainless steel appliances, pantry, and espresso cabinets topped with crown molding.      The split floor plan allows ample privacy for the Master Bedroom and Bathroom. The ensuite features double vanity sink, soaking tub, and walk-in shower. The additional bathroom is shared between the two additional bedrooms.      Sliding doors allow convenient access to the covered, brick patio and spacious fenced in backyard, making this the perfect space to host family and friends all year long. Appenine is located in Narcoossee Village giving you access to all its amenities, including the community pool and playground. When you are not relaxing in the backyard, or enjoying afternoons by the pool, there is no doubt you won’t be enjoying all Lake Nona has to offer. This home is closely located to Orlando International Airport, Lake Nona’s booming town center, Tavistock’s popular restaurants, Boxi Park, The Wave Hotel and its popular restaurants, Bacon, Haven, Nami, shopping amenities, and more!
